SUMMARY:AEGON FUNDING CO LLC — Aegon Investor Call #3
DESCRIPTION:Aegon Ltd investor call. Speakers: Yves Cormier (Global Head of Investor Relations\, Treasury & Ratings)\, Marvin Brizee (Senior Vice President and Head of Group Treasury)\, Lein Pieter Cevaal (Head of Capital Markets Solutions). Registration: https://evercall.co/events/aegon-deal-roadshow-investor-call\nIssuer: AEGON FUNDING CO LLC\nRoadshow: DealRoadshow Details: URL: https://dealroadshow.com | Entry Code: AEGON2026 | Direct Link: https://dealroadshow.com/e/AEGON2026\n\nDeal context:\nAegon Funding Company LLC\, a wholly-owned subsidiary of Aegon Ltd (rated Baa1/BBB+ stable by Moody's/S&P)\, has mandated five joint book-running managers — BofA Securities\, Citigroup\, Deutsche Bank Securities\, Morgan Stanley\, and Wells Fargo Securities — to arrange fixed income investor calls commencing April 28\, 2026\, ahead of a planned benchmark USD-denominated Senior Notes offering due 2036 in SEC registered format. The notes will be guaranteed on a senior unsecured basis by Aegon Ltd and are expected to carry the same Baa1/BBB+ ratings as the parent. No size\, pricing\, or spread guidance has been disclosed at this mandate stage\, with the offering subject to market conditions.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR